Module it.polimi.ingsw.am52
Package it.polimi.ingsw.am52.model.cards

Class Kingdom

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am52.model.cards.Kingdom
public final class Kingdom extends Object
The kingdom of a card. There are four kingdoms, each with its associated resource and color. A kingdom object can be obtained by calling the appropriate static method of this class.
